Parker BUGS -- known bugs. 2004-04-30


* in some ftp site binary "collect" can't finish seaching.
	fixed at 2005-06-30, miss a close after mkstemp
* in some site with ftpd such as glftpd,ls -lR take too many time, and glftpd
	regard list as idle. so when in these site, collect can't finish.
	-r should be used with these site
* the ftpdata that out of date can't be remove automatically.
* if ftp_user & ftp_pass contain "@", the scanline function will be wrong,
* close(ns) and close(hh) in function QueryDir() 
